n levee. 6. Airboats, aircraft, motorized pirogues and go-devils are prohibited in refuge waters. * * * * * Catahoula National Wildlife Refuge * * * * * B. Upland Game Hunting. Hunting of raccoon, squirrel and rabbit is permitted on designated areas of the refuge subject to the following condition: Permits are required. * * * * * D'Arbonne National Wildlife Refuge * * * * * C. Big Game Hunting. * * * 1. Either-sex deer hunting with firearms is permitted for two consecutive days beginning with the second either-sex season in Union Parish and two consecutive days beginning with the third either-sex season. * * * * * Delta National Wildlife Refuge * * * * * D. Sport Fishing. * * * 1. Recreational fishing and crabbing are permitted only from sunrise to sunset. 2. The use of trotlines, limblines, slat traps, gar sets, nets or alligator lines is prohibited. * * * * *
